description:
Happy Mother's Day!
Get it & more music : https://linktr.ee/jehovahshalomacapella

In a special way....
we want to dedicate this song to all amazing Moms!
Whether she's your biological mom or a family friend who is basically your mom, make sure that the most important woman in your life knows how much she's loved.

Mum Elizabeth is the biological-mother to Elijah,Wasswa.A and Kato.
We feel Blessed! To have shared this amazing love with Mommy to other Moms around the World.
